description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. Totally non-scripted, all in front of a live audience, all broadcast live to members. Today's update is RD 1 of 4. This was December's live match now edited for your enjoyment!
This round had everything you have come to love about the non-scripted competitive wrestling here at Ultimate Surrender. Intense one-on-one action and brutal sexual tag team 2 on 1's. All four girls wrestle their asses off for 12 minutes, and at the end of the first round only 1pt separates the two teams.
If you have never seen a non-scripted tag team match before this is the one you want to check out first! Authentic sexual lesbian wrestling, the only of its kind in the world!
title: 4 tough bitches battle in non-scripted Live Tag Team Action
